{"words":[{"word":"everyone","count":4},{"word":"something","count":3},{"word":"looks","count":2},{"word":"i'll","count":2},{"word":"everything","count":2},{"word":"time","count":2},{"word":"light","count":2},{"word":"chaser","count":2},{"word":"collection","count":2},{"word":"photos","count":2},{"word":"course","count":2},{"word":"moments","count":2},{"word":"first","count":2},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"mmm","count":1},{"word":"lovely","count":1},{"word":"photo","count":1},{"word":"sunlight's","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"today","count":1},{"word":"happy","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"terminal","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"organize","count":1},{"word":"pictures","count":1},{"word":"uploaded","count":1},{"word":"submitted","count":1},{"word":"rename","count":1},{"word":"files","count":1},{"word":"add","count":1},{"word":"location","count":1},{"word":"date","count":1},{"word":"quick","count":1},{"word":"caption","count":1},{"word":"check","count":1},{"word":"portrait","count":1},{"word":"permissions","count":1},{"word":"select","count":1},{"word":"capsule","count":1},{"word":"delivery","count":1},{"word":"tag","count":1},{"word":"event","count":1},{"word":"theme","count":1},{"word":"upload","count":1},{"word":"complete","count":1},{"word":"submission","count":1},{"word":"officially","count":1},{"word":"part","count":1},{"word":"graduation","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"appeared","count":1},{"word":"captured","count":1},{"word":"receive","count":1},{"word":"capsules","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"knows","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"incredible","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"rewards","count":1},{"word":"process","count":1},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"royalties","count":1},{"word":"credits","count":1},{"word":"promised","count":1},{"word":"extra","count":1},{"word":"goodies","count":1},{"word":"prepared","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"bread","count":1},{"word":"instant","count":1},{"word":"noodles","count":1},{"word":"jelly","count":1},{"word":"cups","count":1},{"word":"pick","count":1},{"word":"eh","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"full","count":1},{"word":"snack","count":1},{"word":"bundle","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"tight","count":1},{"word":"um","count":1},{"word":"besides","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"personal","count":1},{"word":"yep","count":1},{"word":"senior","count":1},{"word":"passed","count":1},{"word":"joined","count":1},{"word":"fan","count":1},{"word":"club","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"listen","count":1},{"word":"album","count":1},{"word":"sorting","count":1},{"word":"submissions","count":1},{"word":"later","count":1},{"word":"night","count":1},{"word":"seniors","count":1},{"word":"graduated","count":1},{"word":"borrowed","count":1},{"word":"academy's","count":1},{"word":"broadcast","count":1},{"word":"room","count":1},{"word":"played","count":1},{"word":"song","count":1},{"word":"speakers","count":1},{"word":"whole","count":1},{"word":"campus","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"wind","count":1},{"word":"strong","count":1},{"word":"fluttered","count":1},{"word":"sunlight","count":1},{"word":"smiling","count":1},{"word":"brightly","count":1},{"word":"youth","count":1},{"word":"purest","count":1},{"word":"form","count":1},{"word":"playername","count":1},{"word":"entrusting","count":1},{"word":"record","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"keeps","count":1},{"word":"company","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1},{"word":"sings","count":1},{"word":"along","count":1},{"word":"shining","count":1},{"word":"beautiful","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"And… done!","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"...Mmm, what a lovely photo! The sunlight's perfect today. Everyone looks so happy.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Alright, hand me your Terminal. I'll help organize all the pictures and get everything uploaded and submitted.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Let's see… I'll just rename the files, add location and date, a quick caption…","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Check portrait permissions, select \"Time Capsule Delivery,\" and tag the event theme…","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"There! Upload complete!","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"And with that, your submission is officially part of the Light Chaser Collection.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"On graduation day, everyone who appeared in your photos—and of course, you, the one who captured these moments—will all receive your own time capsules.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Hmm, but who knows? By then, you might be somewhere far away, doing something incredible.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Oh! Your rewards should process soon. Royalties, and of course, credits. Everything that was promised.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"As for the extra goodies I prepared—","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"I've got bread, instant noodles, and jelly cups! Pick one!","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Eh?! All of them?!","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Fine! A full snack bundle it is! Here, hold tight!","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"But, um… besides those, there's something else I wanted to give you. Something a bit more… \"personal.\"","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Yep, a senior passed it down to me when I first joined the fan club.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"Back then, I used to listen to this album while sorting through submissions for the very first Light Chaser Collection with everyone.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"And later, the night before our seniors graduated, we borrowed the Academy's broadcast room and played this song over the speakers for the whole campus.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"I still remember. The wind was so strong, and all the photos fluttered in the sunlight. Everyone in them was smiling so brightly…","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"…I think that might be what \"youth\" looks like in its purest form.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"{PlayerName}, I'm entrusting this record to you now.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014},{"text":"I hope it keeps you company in the days ahead, and that it sings along with you through all the shining, beautiful moments to come.","quest_name":"Moments Captured in Light","quest_id":189700014}]}